highlights.text: Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Kolkata. “Jhoome Jo Pathaan” is the highest at #3.
“Labon Ko” by Pritam and KK is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Kolkata, up 40 spots at #40.
“Maan Meri Jaan” by King has been on Top Songs Kolkata the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
“Maan Meri Jaan (Afterlife)” by King and Nick Jonas is the highest new entry on Top Songs Kolkata at #31.
